  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row justify-content-evenly">
      
      <div class="col-3">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
          <img src="https://t3.ftcdn.net/jpg/02/48/42/64/360_F_248426448_NVKLywWqArG2ADUxDq6QprtIzsF82dMF.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">The Value of Experience Design</h5>
            <p class="card-text">XD is about understanding and addressing the needs, emotions, and behaviors of our users. A seamless, intuitive, and delightful user experience can lead to increased user engagement and efficiencies. By incorporating UX principles from the outset, we can identify potential design flaws and user pain points early in the development process. This proactive approach minimizes the chances of costly rework and allows for the delivery of polished products more quickly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-3">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm" >
          <img src="https://t3.ftcdn.net/jpg/02/48/42/64/360_F_248426448_NVKLywWqArG2ADUxDq6QprtIzsF82dMF.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Aligning with Business Goals</h5>
            <p class="card-text">XD efforts are not isolated; they are tightly aligned with our organization's strategic objectives. By incorporating user feedback and data-driven insights, we can fine-tune our products to meet user needs precisely, resulting in a competitive edge and differentiation in the market.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-3">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
          <img src="https://t3.ftcdn.net/jpg/02/48/42/64/360_F_248426448_NVKLywWqArG2ADUxDq6QprtIzsF82dMF.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Enhancing Employee Productivity</h5>
            <p class="card-text">A well-designed user experience isn't limited to external users; it extends to our internal tools and systems. Streamlined and intuitive interfaces empower our employees to work efficiently, reducing training time and minimizing errors.  </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-3">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
          <img src="https://t3.ftcdn.net/jpg/02/48/42/64/360_F_248426448_NVKLywWqArG2ADUxDq6QprtIzsF82dMF.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Measuring Success</h5>
            <p class="card-text">The impact of XD on our business goals is measurable and quantifiable. We track key performance indicators such as user engagement, usefulness and usability improvements. These metrics provide tangible evidence of how XD initiatives directly contribute to our organization's success, enabling us to make informed decisions and investments.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

